title: Harmony Gelish UV Soak Off Gel Polish #324 Simple Sheer
description: This color gel is conveniently designed by "Gelish by Harmony" with a twist cap and applicator brush, apply like polishes, and cured under UV lamp. Color gels are meant to use on natural nails. These products are made to satisfy natural-nail wearers who long wish their color would last for more than two weeks. Color gels will stay on nails for three weeks with no chipping or peeling, and soak completely off in only 15 minutes.

title: Harmony Foundation Base, Top if off and ph Bond - 3 PACK
description: This wonderful set of gel base coat, gel top coat and pH bond provides the basics for any style of manicure or pedicure. Harmony PH Bond is used in the preparation of the nail as a dehydrating step. This product is essential in the proper preparation of the nail plate for optimal performance. Harmony Foundation Base Gel creates the adhesive bond between the nail plate and gel products. This product secures adhesion while not damaging the natural nail plate. Foundation Gel works with Harmony's products as a base for the Soak Off Gel Polishes. Foundation cures in 10 seconds in a LED Light or 30 seconds in an UV Light. Top It Off Gel is a sealer top gel designed to create the ultimate finish with your Soak Off Polish. It creates a high shine that will not dull, chip or peel. Top It Off is a soak off product that can quickly be removed with Soak Off Gel Remover. This coat cures in 30 seconds in a LED Light or 2 minutes in a UV Light.

title: Salon Edge 36W Nail UV Lamp Acrylic Gel Shellac Curing Light Timer 36 Watt Dryer With Slide Out Tray

This unit uses 4 powerful UV bulbs and features a built in timer. Enjoy your FREE sanding file!Effectively and quickly cured all UV and gel based products.Reflective inside lining to ensure proper uniform drying.Fast curing of UV gels one hand at a time.Built in timer with 2 minute setting for perfect time management.Includes easy access panel on bottom to easily change bulbs.Simple fuse replacement compartment with single turn access.Features Salon Edge logo to ensure you recieve the quality you deserve.
